videos.headline: Ware dons turnover robe after 59-yard pick-6
videos.description: Jarvis Ware picks off Kyle Trask and evades the Florida defense for a 59-yard interception touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ware dons turnover robe after 59-yard pick-6) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trask, Toney connect for TDs on consecutive drives
videos.description: Kyle Trask hits Kadarius Toney with a short pass and the WR slips out of the defender's hands for an 18-yard touchdown. After the Florida defense recovers a fumble, Trask finds Toney again with a 30-yard bomb.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trask, Toney connect for TDs on consecutive drives) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mullen gets crowd fired up after Florida-Mizzou brawl
videos.description: Florida QB Kyle Trask suffers a hard hit on the final play of the first half, inciting a brawl between Florida and Missouri. As Dan Mullen returns to the locker room, he asks the crowd to make some noise.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mullen gets crowd fired up after Florida-Mizzou brawl) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toney tiptoes into end zone for 3rd TD
videos.description: Kadarius Toney takes the handoff and tightropes the sideline for a 16-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Toney tiptoes into end zone for 3rd TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Toney shines as Florida steamrolls Mizzou
videos.description: Kadarius Toney catches two touchdowns and runs in another as the Gators dominate on both sides of the ball for a convincing 41-17 win over Missouri.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Toney shines as Florida steamrolls Mizzou) 2020/10/31 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Mullen gives postgame presser as Darth Vader
videos.description: Dan Mullen addresses Florida's halftime brawl with Missouri while dressed as Darth Vader.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Press Conference (Mullen gives postgame presser as Darth Vader) 2020/10/31
